title: Looking for a DuoQ Partner for Diamond rush! (Platin3+)
body:
Hi,
I am looking for a DuoQ Partner for a Diamond rush. I am on vacation right now so I can play all night long! You should be at least Platin4.
My main role is ADC/Top - you can play any role you want ; I prefer you to be Mid/Jungle tho
Just add me in-game (IGN: Wizzh) and we can play right after.
